*There is a framed portrait of actor [[Wikipedia:Will Smith|Will Smith]] in the Bedroom.
*Many of Murder 4's sound effects are from Valve's [[Wikipedia:Left_4_Dead_(franchise)|Left 4 Dead]] series.
*Murder 4 is statistically the most popular game in Jar's "Murder" series.
